data.description: Situated on a one-way street, this Washington Park gem is the perfect fusion of contemporary comfort and timeless charm. Every detail has been carefully considered, from the newer plumbing and electrical systems to the updated kitchens and baths. New roof in 2023 with warranty! As you step inside the duplexed first-floor unit, you'll immediately feel at home in a space that is ideal for both owner occupancy or tenants alike. The four generously sized bedrooms offer ample space for relaxation and privacy, while the spacious living/dining room combo provides an inviting area for entertaining guests. The updated kitchen is a chef's dream with its sleek design and high-end appliances. Venture downstairs to discover a finished basement that offers even more versatility. Complete with an additional full bath and a storage/laundry room with its own separate exit, this lower level provides endless possibilities for customization. The second-floor unit features four inviting bedrooms, along with a cozy living room and dining area. This investor's dream is situated near historic Washington Park, conveniently located between the red and green lines, and within walking distance to the new Jewel-Osco and Obama Library-you can't beat the location! Commuting is a breeze with easy access to the Dan Ryan Expressway, which can get you to downtown Chicago in just 15 minutes or take you to the 59th street beach within 10 minutes. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
